{"title":"连队小曲","authors":["周纲"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":6,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"连队小曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周纲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的脚步那么轻……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的脚步那么轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻得像一朵云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻把战士的被角塞好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像折了一封信；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻把小窗关上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像扣上自己的衣领；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻把炉前的火星踩灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像吹熄了一盏灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的脚步那么轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻得像一朵云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能听见连长的脚音？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有警觉的哨兵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小吴要修桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看老师傅弯钢筋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又轻又快又巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根一根接一根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似编着柳条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他自己拿起搬子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢筋在手里乱跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是长了，就是短了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯了一堆废料！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎！吴明照呀吴明照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你真是糟糕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这小小的钢筋也弯不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭甚么本事修桥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上高楼，地下长廊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦河水闸，浪里钢桥……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要练出灵巧的双手啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把伟大的理想缔造！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他看着面前的图纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又弯着一堆废料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累了，困了，睡了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图上的符号还在梦里跳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根钢筋突然变成桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一列火车在他肩上跑……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他惊醒了，揉揉双眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙拿起枕边的钢条……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎！吴明照呀吴明照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的手呀真正巧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根根坚硬的钢筋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你手里好像软柳条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我，你怎样弯得这样好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子，别害臊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出你的手来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看老茧又添了多少……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1962年3月写于“杨连第连”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}